# City Pollution Risk Score

## Objective
Identify cities with consistently poor air quality to prioritize air purifier market entry.

## Metrics Created
- Average AQI per city
- Number of severe pollution days (AQI ≥ 200)
- Pollution persistence ratio
- Normalized pollution risk score (0–100)

## Business Impact
This score enables leadership to:
- Rank cities by pollution risk
- Identify high-priority markets
- Support data-driven product and marketing strategy
